article.description: Manny Camper recorded 11 points and 12 rebounds to lift Siena to a 61-58 win over St. Peter's on Thursday night, the Saints' seventh straight home victory.
article.headline: Camper lifts Siena over St. Peter's 61-58
article.linkText: Camper lifts Siena over St. Peter's 61-58
article.story: ALBANY, N.Y. -- Manny Camper recorded 11 points and 12 rebounds to lift Siena to a 61-58 win over St. Peter's on Thursday night, the Saints' seventh straight home victory. Jalen Pickett had 16 points and six rebounds for Siena (7-6, 3-1 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Sammy Friday IV added 10 points. Aaron Estrada had 13 points for the Peacocks (5-7, 2-1). KC Ndefo added 7 points and five blocks. Quinn Taylor had seven rebounds. Siena faces Manhattan on the road on Sunday. St. Peter's plays Canisius at home on Sunday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
